# Title: SugusGuard Apple Update Blocklist
# Description: Filterlist to block Apple updates for AdGuard Home / AdGuard Pro App
# List-URL: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SugusGuard/Blocklists/main/SugusGuardAUB
# We use REFUSED;; here, so Apple devices seems to reduce harassing the dns server every few seconds
#
## Prevent filter-bypassing with DoH requests as Apple like to do
#        
||doh.dns.apple.com^$dnsrewrite=REFUSED;;,important
||doh.dns.apple.com.v.aaplimg.com^$dnsrewrite=REFUSED;;,important
#
## Apple Updates & Update-Check iOS, iPadOS, tvOS, and macOS
#
||appldnld.apple.com^$dnsrewrite=REFUSED;;,important
||appldnld.apple.com.akadns.net^$dnsrewrite=REFUSED;;,important
||appldnld-lb.apple.com.akadns.net^$dnsrewrite=REFUSED;;,important
||appldnld.g.aaplimg.com^$dnsrewrite=REFUSED;;,important
||mesu.apple.com^$dnsrewrite=REFUSED;;,important
